FBIS4-10897 "drlat076_a_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-076 Daily Report 19 Apr 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Raul Castro Attends Western Army Military Council Raul Castro Attends Western Army Military Council FL2004011294 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 2300 GMT 19 Apr 94 FL2004011294 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Spanish BFN [Text] Army General Raul Castro Ruz, second secretary of the Cuban Communist Party Central Committee, and defense minister of the Cuban Revolutionary Armed Forces, is attending work sessions of the special military council of the Eastern Army, which is analyzing the experience of this unit in using alternative energy sources. This council is also discussing the efforts being made to save fuel, at the same time outlining directives to intensify the energy program in military units.
